column2: SELECT m.SPRC, m.Objid, m.R, m.cz, p.objid, p.ra, p.dec, p.dered_u, p.dered_g, p.dered_r, p.dered_i, p.dered_z, s.class, s.subclass, g.specObjID , s.specObjID, s.z as redshift, g.h_beta_flux, g.oiii_#_flux, g.h_alpha_flux, g.nii_#_flux into SPRC_dr8_with_data from dr8.PhotoObjAll AS p JOIN dr1#.SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid JOIN MyDB.SPRC_dr8 AS m ON m.Objid = p.objid JOIN dr1#.galSpecLine AS g ON s.specObjID = g.specObjID
